5
00:04:39.560 --> 00:04:43.087
<i>Ceres was once covered in ice.</i>

6
00:04:43.880 --> 00:04:46.804
<i>Enough water for 1. 000 generations.</i>

7
00:04:47.360 --> 00:04:52.127
