40
00:06:34.920 --> 00:06:37.321
<i>See you then.</i> welwala.

41
00:06:38.200 --> 00:06:41.329
What is <i>welwala?</i>

42
00:06:43.200 --> 00:06:45.043
"Traitor to my people."

43
